title: "The Accepted Whispers" is a compilation of over 200 supplications (duas) from the Quran and Hadith, compiled by Mawlana Ashraf Ali Thanawi and translated and commented upon by Khalid Baig. The book is structured for daily reading, with supplications organized by days of the week, starting from Saturday and ending with Friday. Each day includes a series of duas, along with their Arabic text, transliteration, translation, and commentary to help readers understand the significance and context of each supplication.
